      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER SEAPLANE (5) has a strong overall record having five wins and seven places from 15 starts including a last start third (24.22) over 407m at Rockhampton. Has never missed the frame at the trip from five starts. Happy to have him on top this line-up. MAGIC MYSTERY (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths third (19.87) over 352m at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Leading player again. BIZZARO BOY (2) jumped well and was in the mix early before fading out of it late when 6th over 352m at this track in Grade 3/4 company. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Leading chance. BUSH BOODIE (3) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.",
